  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de Kde-baseapps</title>

    <para>Installez <application>Kde-baseapps</application> en lançant les commandes
    suivantes&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd build &amp;&amp;
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=$KDE4_PREFIX \
      -DKDE_DEFAULT_HOME=.kde4 \
      -DSYSCONF_INSTALL_DIR=/etc/kde4 \
      .. &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>
